<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1> 
    <p>Last Updated:  March 7, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect account information, usage data, uploaded content, and device information.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>We use data to provide, maintain, and improve the Services, ensure security, and comply with legal obligations.</p>

    <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We share data only with service providers, authorized integrations, and legal authorities when required.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain data only as long as necessary to provide the Services or meet legal requirements.</p>

    <h2>5. Security</h2>
    <p>We use encryption, access controls, and continuous monitoring to protect your data.</p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may have rights to access, correct, delete, or export your data depending on your jurisdiction.</p>

    <h2>7. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>The Services are not intended for children under 18.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: support@insighthunter.app</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
